src/vec.rs:61     static pure fn make(&&x:float, &&y:float, &&z:float) -> self;
                  ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
error: aborting due to 2 previous errors
```
